打包格式

数据包
 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
+---------------------------------------------------------------+-+-+------------+-------------------------------+-------------------------------+
|                              size                             |h|t|  extcode   |             route             |              seq              |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+-+-+------------+-------------------------------+-------------------------------+
|                                                                trace context(25字节) ...                                                        |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                message data ...                                                                |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

trace context 固定长度25字节：TraceID 16字节 + SpanID 8字节 + TraceFlags 1字节

握手(handshake)和心跳(heartbeat)没有加链路追踪信息